                        @{u}Bugs and Limitations@{uu}

 o The program can only be started once at a time. The reason is probably an error in the screennotify.library (?) resulting in the effect that only one ThumbMail-window receives the message to close its window. This results in a deadlock. Hello, Stefan, have a look at this. ;-)

 o The screennotify.library seems to lock up sometimes when trying to close the screen. Seems to be not our fault, but we will try to fix it anyway.

 o Really serious bugs are not known to us, they have all been smashed.

 Nevertheless, in case you discover a bug, do not hesitate to contact @{"us" link "e_Autoren" 0}.

@endnode


